
## Page Up/Down "scroll" instead of navigating whole pages
map [normal]     <PageUp>   scroll half-up
map [normal]     <PageDown> scroll half-down
map [fullscreen] <PageUp>   scroll half-up
map [fullscreen] <PageDown> scroll half-down

## Disable all guioptions (no statusbar, messagebar, or scrollbars)
set guioptions ""

## Adjust default size to DIN A4 format
set window-width 800
set window-height 1142 ## (1132 + slack)

## Copy into X clipboard
set selection-clipboard "clipboard"

## In dual-page mode, the first page is a *left* page
set first-page-column 1

